divs: sighting details i was in the back yard with my dog and i looked up and saw this white orb for a few seconds and then it disapeared. a few weeks later i was out back and i looked up again and there where two orbs traveling together to the south and when they got about 2 or 3 miles to the south they stopped and the one on the left went to the east for about a 1\4 of a mile and the other one waited until it came back and then they continued traveling south south west and dissapeard. the next time i saw them was about a month later. i was sitting at the computer and i heard a jet coming by really loud so i knew it was real low and i didn't think to much about it. so about 5 or 10 minutes later i heard the jet coming back so i got up and walked outside to see what was going on. by that time the jet was about a mile to the south and to the right of the jet was a single orb they continued on to the south. that is my story and i have seen them since. i still look up every time i go outside at night hopping they will return,but no luck yet.thank you
